                     <interp inst="t18260914-415-person2149" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am headborough. I went with Bellamy to her house, on the 7th of August; I found the prisoner there drunk - I took him to the watch-house - I said I must search him - and he gave me two duplicates of a sheet and a piece of cotton.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-415-person2150">
                  GEORGE 
                  JOHN BOLTON
               <interp inst="t18260914-415-person2150" type="surname" value="JOHN BOLTON"></interp>
